						final information has been received and prepared by Lazarus, then each 
						prospective buyer receives a business profile of each successful match.
					






Valuation


						We perform a professional business valuation that will assist you in analyzing 
						the financial scope of your business. This valuation will give you an 
						indication of the value of the entity, and be helpful in any buy/sell 
						transactions.
					






Advertising


